    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                
                <p>The family at <placeName ref="pl0001">Downing</placeName>, <persName ref="pe0814">Bride</persName> &amp; 
                    <persName ref="pe0065">Bridegroom</persName> included, present their best compliments &amp; thanks to 
                    <persName ref="pe0803">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Lloyd</persName> for his friendly and handsome congratulations. 
                    M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> P.<note type="editorial">This could refer to either Thomas Pennant or to his son, David.</note> 
                    returns particular thanks for the hunted hare.</p>
                
                
                <closer><dateline><placeName ref="pl0001">Downing</placeName> Dec<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> 23<hi rend="superscript">d</hi>. 1793</dateline>
                </closer>
            </div>
            
